    Class Description
    Application
    Driver class for the Harry Potter package with GridController.
    Attack
    Command to attack entities.
    AttackInformation  
    AttackNeighbours  
    Capability
    Capabilities that various entities may have.
    DeathEater  
    Dumbledore
    Dumbledore At this stage, he's an extremely strong critter with a Sword who wanders around in a fixed pattern and neatly slices any Actor not on his team with his sword.
    HPAction
    Base class for all intransitive commands/Actions in the harrypotter world.
    HPActionInterface
    Interface that allows HPAction and HPAffordance to have a common ancestor (and thus be stored in the same structures) despite one extending Action and the other extending Affordance.
    HPActor  
    HPAffordance
    Class that represents Affordances in the harrypotter world.
    HPEntity
    Class that represents inanimate objects in the Harry Potter world.
    HPEntityInterface
    All Entities and Actors in the harrypotter client package should implement this interface.
    HPGrid
    Grid of HPLocations.
    HPGridController
    Concrete implementation of the GridController.
    HPGridTextInterface
    This is the text based user interface for the simulation.
    HPLegend
    This class represents "legends" - major characters - in the Harry Potter universe.
    HPLocation
    Class that models locations in Harry Potter.
    HPLocation.HPLocationMaker
    Factory class used by Grids to instantiate HPLocations
    HPWorld
    Class representing a world in the Harry Potter universe.
    Move
    HPAction that lets HPActors walk around the map.
    Patrol  
    Player
    A very minimal HPActor that the user can control.
    Sword
    A sword
    Take
    HPAction that lets a HPActor pick up an object.
    Team
    Enumerator class for different types of Teams for the HPActors.
    TestActor
    A very minimal HPActor that just describes the scene.
    TextInterface
    IMPORTANT This UI is no longer required and is not compatible with the controller.
